(74030, 225452, 0, 1, '03 - Will You Change For Love.wav', 'Will You Change For Love 您可願為愛而改變(這個世界)?\n\n人生一路走來, 經歴了許多苦與樂, 在跑船的那段日子裡, 親眼目睹了多少辛酸的政事,  人事, 地物. 所以我在此歌曲的開端就問: 啊! 人們, 為什麼您們仍在受苦之中? 為什麽這個世界上仍充斥了許多飢荒? 為什麼許多人們仍照樣的壓迫他人?\n貪婪使我們成為欺瞞者及說謊者(就像是所有的政客或所謂的菁英), 瞋恨使我們成為毀滅者(不至毁減他人, 毀滅了自巳), 癡則使我們麻木, 無知.\n*這就是佛所說的: 衆生的三毒 貪, 嗔, 癡.\n\n您可願給愛一個機會? 拋棄毒化我們靈魂的三毒, 分享您的愛心予衆生, 六道衆生是和我們相同的, 他們和我們一樣也都有靈性的. 我們能使這個世界變得更好, 成為天堂, 您可願為愛而改變這個世界?\n\n在第二段時, 我向所有國家的國父提出問題: 為什麼我們仍然有許多戰事? 為什麽我們仍在製造更大更爆裂的炸彈? 我們巳幾平能醫治所有的疾病,為什麼我們不拿來治癒整個世界? 權力, 您能握持多久?, 金錢: 它真能帶給您真心的快樂嗎? 殺戮真的能帶來和平嗎? 您可願意給” 愛” 一個機會?\n\n我在橫批(Bridge) 寫著: 我們不需要貪, 瞋, 癡三毒, 用愛,關懷及分享, 則我們可以改變這個世界, 使它成為一個真正的天堂!\n\n這是一曲正統的搖滚樂, 希望它有一天能將這世上所有沉睡的人們搖醒, 並用愛心來改變所有的恨. 這個世界才有希望.\n', '2013-08-04 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 0, 1, 'Will You Change For Love      By: Jimmy Jang\nVerse 1:\nOh! People…. \nWhy do we still suffer?  \nWhy does the world still hunger?\nWhy are people still abusing each other? \nGreed, makes us become liars & cheaters.\nAnger, makes us become destroyers.\nStupor, that makes us Ignorant!\n\nChorus:\n\nWill you change and give love a chance?\nDrop the poisons of your soul!\nShare your love with all.\nWe are one, we are all.\nWe’d make this world wondrous.\nThe Paradise!\n\nVerse 2:\n\nOh! Fathers\nWhy do we still have wars?\nWhy do we still build bigger bombs?\nWhy don’t we cure all the world’s ills?\nPower: how long can you hold it?\nMoney: Can it bring you happiness?\nKilling: Does it truly bring you peace?\n\nChorus:\nWill you change and give love a chance?\nDrop the poisons of your soul!\nShare your love with all.\nWe are one, we are all.\nWe’d make this world wondrous.\nThe Paradise!\n\nBridge:\nNo need: Greed, Anger, and Stupor.\nCaring, Sharing for all with love.\nWe will change this earth \nInto a paradise!\n\nChorus:\nWill you change and give love a chance?\nDrop the poisons of your soul!\nShare your love with all.\nWe are one, we are all.\nWe’d make this world wondrous.\nThe Paradise! (Fade out)\n', '', 221, '', 'Jimmy Jang', 'Jimmy Jang', 'Harry King and Jimmy Jang', 'Monday Rose (ASCAP)', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-04-09 07:47:40', '2015-03-12 14:06:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(74031, 225452, 0, 1, '06 - Hold Me Now.wav', 'Hold Me Now  擁抱著我\n什麼樣的愛人會讓您刻苦銘心?\n今生有幾次您親自邂逅?\n\n己經過了幾個酷寒, 但每次到紐約時心中不時的希望能再一次的再見她一面, 即使隔一條街的望著她, 也可以療這情傷! \n\n為什麼人總是要等到” 失去後”, 才會回想, 那才是我這一生最需要的伴侶? 為什麽我們在” 擁有後”不去珍惜? 曾多次的刺傷對方的心, 卻一次又一次的執著自大, 直到今世緣已盡, 情己了, 才覺悟到原來” 真愛” 是如此的深, 才知對方內心的苦處, 但人, 事以非, 若人生可以再來一次, 我會跪下來求她留下, 而不再放蕩.\n\n擁抱著我 Hold Me Now, 這是給我最深愛的破碎之情人, 心中想傾訴的一句話.\n可惜, 經費有限,不然會拍一微電影(音樂短片M.V) 也希望和您們分享.\n\n更希望您們能閉著眼, 聆聽這首情歌\n', '2013-08-04 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 0, 1, 'Hold   Me   Now                 By Jimmy Jang\nVerse 1:\nI’d  get down on my knees, if that could get you back!\nYour Love is all I need, to pass through this world.\nI knew you’ve been hurt by me, but your heart always with me.\nNow you have gone away, and left me with Emptiness.\n\nChorus:\nHold me now!   Don’t leave me lonely.\nCan’t you see, I can’t live without you.\nHold me now! Don’t ever leave me.\nYou are my destiny.  My one and only.  \nHere in my heart.\n\nVerse 2:\nI promised  to be  with you, whenever you needed me.\nThe lies I made to you, have come back to haunt me.\nNow  that you’ve  gone  away, life turned  to misery\nAll the love we shared, turn into memories. \n\nChorus:\nHold me now! Don’t leave me lonely.\nCan’t you see, I can’t live without you\nHold me now! Don’t ever leave me.\nYou are my destiny. My one and only.  \nHere in my heart.\n\nBridge:\nYou are my night and day, water and air for my life.\nYou are my happiness, sweetness, tenderness in my mind.\nYou are my everything I’m fighting for, in this life. \nYou are my guiding star shining through in the dark night.\nYou are my Angel!\n\nChorus:\nSo! Hold me now!   Don’t leave me lonely.\nCan’t you see, I can’t live without you.\nHold me now! Don’t ever leave me.\nYou are my destiny.  My one and only.  \nHere in my heart. (fade out)\n\n', '', 246, '', 'Jimmy Jang', 'Jimmy Jang', 'Harry King and Jimmy Jang', 'Monday Rose (ASCAP)', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-04-09 07:54:11', '2015-03-12 14:06:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
