(74035, 225452, 0, 1, '07 - Truth Of Love.wav', 'Truth Of Love   真摰的愛\n這是我於2012年底所創作的, 主要是想藉這一首歌來鼓勵人們, 不要輕易的放棄生命, 由其是失戀後, 或者承受壓力等, 另外男, 女感情方面, 希望您們都能找到這一生的” 靈魂伴侶”(Soulmate), 而不是隨處吐痰般的亂愛.\n\n什麼是” 靈魂伴侶”(Soulmate)?, 大意來說, 就是對方的心, 完全的牽繫在你(妳) 的身上, 同時你(妳) 的心也完全的牽繫在對方的身上, 當雙方同時遭遇同一情境時, 雙方的認知, 覺受, 思惟, 在不必開口討論, 就己有內心中的溝通, 或完全覺知對方的想法(心有靈犀一點通) 就是最好的寫照.\n\n真摯的愛, 沒有貧, 富, 殘, 全, 膚色之分, 惟也愛的付出(偶爾也會收受), 若您所交往的對方並不是真心的愛您的話, 不妨放下這種關係, 活著自在些. 若您的生活中沒有愛慕對向, 不如充實自巳, 或當個照顧老, 幼的義工, 提昇自巳的信心, 想必您自己知道該如何生活下去. 要知每個人都有某種程度的傷感, 只要把它” 放下”, 並讓陽光進入您的心懷, 這是個簡單的動作,, 請信任您的心. 倘若您的愛是真摯的, 那您也不會受人愚弄.\n\n不知您們可常有機會去看看天上的星辰? 可知您屬於那一顆? 有否時間去探討”人生的真諦”( 可別玩電玩連續36小時, 把自己玩完了!), 是否曾聆聽發自內心” 愛” 的聲音? 因為您的心聲永遠不會欺瞞您自已(但是您的頭腦常會欺瞞您的, 這就是” 自欺欺人”).\n\n第二段, 來吧, 打起精神, 不要悲觀, 結合您,我的愛, 並成為我的”靈魂伴侶”, 讓我們一起分享理想, 讓我們團結在一起, 解開您心中的鎖鍊吧, 愛它是沒有終點的. 懷\n著您的理想, 絕不放棄, 往前方看, 沒有必要再回頭. 做您自已, 不要做別人的陰影. 並向著您的目標邁進, 在心裹有一處愛的園地屬於您和我.\n\nChrous 2:\n您可知道我們都是第一名, 出生在這個世界上! (您若在國中,有上過健康教育教學裡的影片中, 有上千萬甚至上億的精子, 奮勇的向卵子游去, 其中還要經過, 酸, 鹼的嚴格考驗, 並成為第一個”或同時的兩個, 即雙胞胎”, 的Gentleman(尖頭鰻) 或尖頭妞, 並擊敗了上億的追求者, 而孕育了今天的您. 想一想您可是一為不折不扣的冠軍, 那還有什麽想不開, 過不了難關的). 只要您跟隨您心中的熱情, 用” 愛” 去推動, 去成功. 您可曾聽過您心中那” 愛” 的聲音? 因為您的心就是那” 愛”的地方.\n\n(橫批)Bridge: 啊! 請聆聽您的心聲, 它是為” 愛” 而跳動.\n              您聽見了嗎? 您是否聽到了?\n              心所傾訴的都是真誠的, 也是真摯愛的園地!\n\n所以當我們失去所愛的人, 或失意或失戀時, 或承受巨大壓力時, 請想想這些事, 或錯失等, 是不是自己的貪, 嗔, 癡所造成的? 可別忘記” 留著青山在, 不怕沒柴燒”, 更何況您和我都是第一名的冠軍, 降生來到這個世上, 只要用心, 少雜念, 勿貪, 則人生圓滿!  獻給您們.\n', '2013-08-04 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 0, 7, 'THE   TRUTH   OF   LOVE     \nVerse 1:\nYeah…. Break it off, If the love is not true.            \nCause, Finding true love is hard to do! \nCut her loose, and set yourself free.\nLive without love, than you know what to do.\nWe all have, some bitter blues.\nJust drop it now, let the sun shine through.\nTrust your heart, it’s a simple move!\nIf your love is true, than you won’t be a fool.\nChorus 1:\nHave you ever taken a chance to look to the stars above,\nand spend sometimes in seeking the truth?      \nDid you ever listen to the voices of your heart of love?\nCause your heart is the Truth of Love\n Verse 2:\nCome-on…Cheer up now, no need to be sad!\nUnited in love and be my soul-mate.\nShare your dreams, United we Stand.\nUnchain your heart, Love has no end!\nHold your dreams. Don’t  ever give up.\nLook ahead, you don’t need to look back.\nBe yourself, and reach for the top.\nThere’s a place for love for you and me.\nChorus 2: \nDo you know everyone was born as number 1 (one), in this world?\nFollow your passions and put love to work!\nDid you ever listen to the voices of your heart of love?\nCause your heart; is the Place for Love!\nBridge:  So… Listen to your heart!  Beating for the Love!\n             Did you hear it?    Wow…... Did you feel it?\n             It’s the Truth…Yeah… The Truth of Love…….\nChorus 1 & 2 :\nHave you ever taken a chance to look to the stars above,\nand spend sometimes in seeking the truth?      \nDid you ever, listen to the voices of your heart of love?                                                               \nCause your heart is the Truth of Love.                                                   \nDo you know everyone was born as number 1 (one), in this world?                                                    \nFollow your passions and put love to work!\nDid you ever listen to the voices of your heart of love?\nCause your heart; is the place for Love\nCause your heart, is the Place for Love . \n', '', 222, '', 'Jimmy Jang', 'Jimmy Jang', 'Harry King and Jimmy Jang', 'Monday Rose (ASCAP)', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-04-09 08:06:20', '2015-03-12 14:06:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(74036, 225452, 0, 1, '08 - Love You Tonight.wav', 'Love You Tonight今宵愛妳\n這是一首我在2013年所作的歌曲, 它細述著二年前的一段戀情.\n\n這段戀情分手的主要原因是因為兩造各有各的堅持, 而我本身則是”自我” 的絕不退讓而造成這一切.\n\n在分手的時刻, 她的口中雖然也是硬著嘴皮說: 我對你己不再關心, 從今以後永不再見面. 然而在當時我從她的眼中看到的是一雙淚眼, 欲言又止. 當時的我卻咬咬牙耍帥, 掉頭而去.\n\n事過兩年後, 有天在夢中又相會一起, 分手情景相同, 但這次我願放下”自我”, 願再次的擁抱她, 撫平她的情殤與痛楚, 讓我”今宵愛妳”, 並希望她能再次像從前一樣的擁抱著我, 並將心事告訴我, 一切又是多麼美好, 醒來方知是夢一場.\n\n以此曲獻與所有的情人, 當你/妳真正的從內心愛上一個人時, 千萬勿隨便使脾氣或耍帥, 用心去愛, 去關懐, 愛一個人, 就是耍” 心疼對方”,” 無怨無悔” 則Love is Foreve!\n', '2013-08-04 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 0, 1, 'LOVE YOU TONIGHT    \nVerse 1: \nYou  may  say   you  don’t  care…\nYou  can  live  without   me  there\nBut,  when  I  look  into  your  eyes,  BABY\nI  can  see   how  sad  you  are  inside!\nChorus:\nLet  me  take  you  in  my  arms,  ease  your  pains &  harms\nHold  you  tonight.   Oh! Baby,  Baby…\nLet  love  shine  into  our  heart,  \nnothing  will  tear  us  apart.\nHold  me  tonight.\nCome  on  Girl  gonna  be  alright,  \nlet’s  make  love; we’ll never  fight.                 \nTell me  what  your  feeling  deep  inside.\nLet  me  love  you  tonight.\nVerse 2: \nWhen  you  said  this  is  the  end,\nTrue  love  is  just  like  suicide.\nBut, Before we  kiss  and  say  Good-Bye,  Baby..\nLet’s let the tears from your eyes subside.\nChorus: \nLet  me  take  you  in  my  arms,  ease  your  pains &  harms\nHold  you  tonight.   Oh! Baby,  Baby…\nLet  love  shine  into  our  heart,  \nnothing  will  tear  us  apart.\nHold  me  tonight.\nCome  on  Girl  gonna  be  alright,  \nlet’s  make  love; we’ll never  fight.                 \nTell me  what  your  feeling  deep  inside.\nLet  me  love  you  tonight.\nBridge:  Let me hold you, touch you and build the world around you.\n              Let me cherish you, love you and share my live with you\n              Hum…. Yeah…\nChorus: \nBaby,  Baby,  Baby… \nLet  me  take  you  in  my  arms,  ease  your  pains &  harms\nHold  you  tonight.   Oh! Baby,  Baby…\nLet  love  shine  into  our  heart,  \nnothing  will  tear  us  apart.\nHold  me  tonight.\nCome  on  Girl  gonna  be  alright,  \nlet’s  make  love; we never fight.\nTell me  what  your  feeling  deep  inside.  \nCome  on  Girl  gonna  be  alright,  \nlet’s  make  love; till the morning light\nTell me  what  your  feeling  deep  inside.\nLet me love you  tonight.\nEnding: You  may  say   you  don’t  care…\n              You  can  live  without   me  there… \n', '', 238, '', 'Jimmy Jang', 'Jimmy Jangj', 'Harry King and Jimmy Jang', 'Monday Rose (ASCAP)', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-04-09 08:10:10', '2015-03-12 14:06:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(74037, 225452, 0, 1, '09 - You Are The Angel.wav', 'You are the Angel 您就是那天使\n\n這是我在2012年4月間從世界日報(聯合報系北美版) 及李安導演投書一英文雜誌上所看到的一則有關台灣, 台東的慈悲天使” 陳樹菊女士” 的故事, 同年7月初又從印度日報英文版看到一篇有關一初生三天的女嬰, 因為其父窮困無法向省立醫院繳付三美元(折合台幣不到一百元) 來治療”蘋菓臉” 紫外線照射. 正因如此省醫院的醫生决定嘸錢免共(沒錢免談) 不醫, 任由其父母怎麼跪求. 可憐小女嬰三天後死亡. 這事件正巧有一位電視女記者當時採訪醫院而注意到此事,在第四天去探訪窮父母時才發覺這新聞真事(媒體是應如此挖掘真象, 而非擬於上級壓力而做假)\n\n醫生若沒”醫德”, 在印度人命的不值錢, 階級的劃分, 高教育者的貪婪嘴臉等帶給我的靈感而寫下這首Hip Hop饒舌版的” 您就是天使”.\n\n“陳樹菊女士” 小學程度, 學歷不商, 家境窮因, 因緣聚滙, 發菩提(薩)心腸, 捐出絕大部份賣菜所得, 嘉惠多少同樣清寒學子, 鄉里, 其行猶如天主教封聖的    德莉薩修女, 兩者無怨無悔的付出, 得天神所敬仰.\n\n反觀多少的印度醫生(不只印度, 臺灣及中國包括歐美皆有), 高學歴, 亳宅, 名車, 美女, 藝術品, 保鏢及一切用於抬高自身身份, 聲名的品項, 什麽都有, 就是” 醫德兩字沒有! 三美元, 得先付錢否則就挫在那裡等吧. (台灣有句話:反正別人的小孩死不光的, 不干我事), 想想很慶幸今天我們都生在寶島, 台灣, 多麼幸福.\n\n另外, 我必須特別提到的一群富有愛心,有醫德的醫生們,” 無國界醫師”, 同樣的擁有高學歷,卻完全的投入濟生救人的情操, 這些都像” 台灣的陳樹菊女士” 一般, “您就是天使”.\n\n我在結尾裡批: 唯有純真的人性, 這世上才有希望. 別讓金錢使你變成貪腐的禿鷹, 請將您們的愛心分享予所有的衆生, 則我們的世界會成為有道德的世界, 您就是天使, 覺醒吧, 人們.\n', '2013-08-04 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 0, 2, 'You are the Angel              By Jimmy Jang\nAngel! Angel!\nThere’s a lady who struck my heart!\nShe wakes up at 2 and she works so hard.\nShe has little education but with the greatest heart!\nShe sells little vegies and keeps little profit for her part.\nShe donates most her money to the poor who are hit so hard.\nThis is the lady who has Cosmic Mother’s Heart! \nWho is also respected by God! Respected by God! Respected by God! Yeah.\nShe looks very tiny and she makes little money,\nShe talks a little funny and you’ll feel like she’s your granny,\nWhen she gave all her money and people asked: \nWhat is your name lady? And she wanted “Anonymous”.\nHave a Heart, that what I got!\nHave a heart, Respected by God!\nThis is what I’d like to sing for her & Mother Teresa:\n\nChorus:\nYou are the Angel,   you light up humanity for this world.\nTo warm our heart, to ease our pains, to heal our wounded soul\nYou are the Angel, you are everything we have respect for.\nTo share with love, to build up our strength and make our life wonderful\nYou’re the angel heart.\n\nVerse 2:\nThere is a doctor, who is not a “Doctor without Border” \nWho has a lot of money and all the sexy girls, they all call him honey.\nHe has high education but lives without heart!\nHe’s working in the hospital and bought plenty of Art.\nCruising with a sexy driver and 2 body guards\nThere was a new born baby who needed a light cure treatment,\nThe poor baby’s parents couldn’t pay the 3 dollars,\nSo they beg the doctor, please save their child\nAnd the doctor said: You got to make the payment \nBefore I give any treatment! \n3 days later the baby went to the Heaven! \nWhere is your heart! Doctor?\nWhere is your Soul? \nI like to sing this song for the Lady and Doctors without Boarder:\n\nChorus:\nYou are the Angel,   you light up humanity for this world.\nTo warm our heart, to ease our pains, to heal our wounded soul\nYou are the Angel, you are everything we have respect for.\nTo share with love, to build up our strength and make our life wonderful\nYou’re the angel heart.\n\nEnding:\nHumanity’s only hope for the human future,\nDon’t let money’s value turn you into a vulture,\nShare your love with the all of creation and make this world full of wonderful virtues.\nYou are the Angel,\nYou are the Angel! (END)\n\n \n', '', 276, '', 'Jimmy Jang', 'Jimmy Jang', 'Harry King and Jimmy Jang', 'Monday Rose (ASCAP)', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-04-09 08:15:30', '2015-03-12 14:06:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
